<h2>About Me</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<a href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/03751919158717682336'><img alt='My Photo' class='profile-img' height='80' src='http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_VOgQl2P9kDs/Sv3Mh_-gyVI/AAAAAAAAAjY/6jgbfY8iKIc/S220/Pic+for+Blog+2-3.jpg' width='59'/></a>
<dl class='profile-datablock'>
<dt class='profile-data'>
<a class='profile-name-link' href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/03751919158717682336' rel='author'>
Jennie
</a>
</dt>
<dd class='profile-data'>
</dd>
<dd class='profile-textblock'>I'm a 20 something Briton currently living in Germany. I love food and I love photography. I have a huge collection of cookbooks along with many recipes that I have created and collected over the years. Eating a healthy balanced diet is important to me; however, I do believe that one should let their hair down every now and again. So, this blog is a fun mixture of all things healthy, exotic and down right delicious! Join me and my camera on a journey of exploration into the world of culinary delights.</dd>
</dl>
